projects.name: FriendPost
projects.description: FriendPost is a full stack app I built using React, GraphQL, Apollo, MongoDB, NodeJS, and Semantic UI. It's a place for friends to socialize and post their thoughts.

projects.name: ReCaller
projects.description: ReCaller allows you to schedule phone calls with other people and have your conversations transcribed with DeepGram's speech recognition technology. I worked on a team with four other engineers to build this application.

projects.name: Mentor Me
projects.description: Mentor Me connects people with questions to people with answers. I worked primarily as the back end dev for this project. Users can create a secure account, post questions, and post answers.
